OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Anthony
OL,7,FFrance
OL,9,FAirline passengers are being urged not
OL,10,Fto pack power banks in their hold
OL,11,Fluggage because of the fire risk ahead
OL,12,Fof the busy summer holiday travel
OL,13,Fperiod.
OL,15,FLithium batteries are now the number
OL,16,Fone safety risk to aircraft, the Civil
OL,17,FAviation Authority regulator said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
