FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FMany travellers use power banks to
OL,7,Fkeep their electronic devices such as
OL,8,Fmobile phones, vapes and laptops
OL,9,Fcharged while they are away from home.
OL,11,FTheir batteries store a relatively
OL,12,Flarge amount of energy in a small
OL,13,Fspace, and when faulty can cause
OL,14,Faggressive fires which spread quickly.
OL,16,FThe average person now takes four
OL,17,Fdifferent lithium-powered devices
OL,18,Fonboard a jet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FIt is generally more straightforward
OL,7,Ffor flight crews to respond to fires
OL,8,Finside the cabin than in the hold,
OL,9,Fprompting Friday's CAA alert.
OL,11,FHow dangerous are lithium-powered
OL,12,Fbanks on flights?
OL,14,FLast month, a London Luton-bound
OL,15,FeasyJet flight had to divert to Rome
OL,16,Fbecause it emerged a passenger's power
OL,17,Fbank had been packed in the hold.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FIn October, a video was widely shared
OL,7,Fof flames belching from the overhead
OL,8,Fstorage compartment of an Air China
OL,9,Fflight after a reported lithium
OL,10,Fbattery fire.
OL,12,FHow many incidents have there been on
OL,13,FUK flights?
OL,15,FThe CAA said reports of overheating or
OL,16,Fmalfunctioning passenger devices
OL,17,Fnearly doubled from 123 in 2024 to 206
OL,18,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
