FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FCases of lithium battery-powered
OL,7,Fdevices being incorrectly packed in
OL,8,Fhold luggage rose 91 per cent over the
OL,9,Fsame period, from 316 incidents to 643.
OL,11,FIt is running a campaign to highlight
OL,12,Fthe threat.
OL,14,FWhat do the major airlines say about
OL,15,Fthe problem?
OL,17,FBritish Airways told ITV News that all
OL,18,Fdevices with lithium batteries in
OL,19,Fchecked hold baggage must be
OL,20,Fcompletely switched off, not in sleep
OL,21,For hibernation mode.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
