FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FSmart luggage tags, such as Apple
OL,7,FAirTag, may remain energised in the
OL,8,Fhold, providing they have smaller
OL,9,Flithium batteries.
OL,11,FIn hand baggage only, up to two power
OL,12,Fbanks per person are allowed. Spare
OL,13,Fbatteries must be carried in the
OL,14,Fcabin. None may exceed a 100 Watt-hour
OL,15,Fenergy limit.
OL,17,FEasyJet's rules state that power banks
OL,18,Fare accepted on aircraft in cabin
OL,19,Fbaggage only, but are prohibited from
OL,20,Fuse and "must not be used to charge
OL,21,Fother devices".
OL,26,@|D@IOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
