FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FVirgin Atlantic's Gareth Salt, vice
OL,7,Fpresident of health, safety and
OL,8,Fsecurity, said: "It's really important
OL,9,Fthat customers know the guidance for
OL,10,Flithium battery-powered devices,
OL,11,Fincluding power banks and vapes, and
OL,12,Fpack them correctly.
OL,14,F"We're proud to support the CAA's
OL,15,F'Pack Right for a Safe Flight'
OL,16,Fcampaign, helping to raise awareness
OL,17,Fof the simple steps customers can take
OL,18,Fto reduce risk and ensure every
OL,19,Fjourney is as safe and enjoyable as
OL,20,Fpossible."
OL,26,@pD@QOUvD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FAre any particular products to blame?
OL,8,FWhile most devices with these
OL,9,Fbatteries are very safe, experts blame
OL,10,Fsubstandard versions bought through
OL,11,Fthird-party sellers that usually
OL,12,Fcaused these overheating problems.
OL,14,FCAA director of aviation safety
OL,15,FGiancarlo Buono said: "Pack right for
OL,16,Fa safe flight, and that means don't
OL,17,Fput your batteries in your checked
OL,18,Fbag. Take them into the cabin with you.
OL,26,@wD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
