OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,F"This simple tip will make your flight
OL,7,Fsafer for you, and the other
OL,8,Fpassengers you're flying with."
OL,10,FA survey of passengers indicated that
OL,11,F36 per cent are unaware of the dangers
OL,12,Fof packing batteries in checked
OL,13,Fbaggage.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
