OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FIt also suggested people take an
OL,7,Faverage of four lithium powered
OL,8,Fdevices on trips, which equates to
OL,9,Fmore than 2,000 on a busy Airbus A380
OL,10,Fflight.
OL,12,FTim Alderslade, chief executive of
OL,13,FAirlines UK, which represents
OL,14,Fcarriers, described the increase in
OL,15,Fthe use of lithium batteries as "a
OL,16,Fgrowing challenge" for the aviation
OL,17,Findustry.
OL,26,@wD@aOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
