OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782514094
OL,3,CCan I pack my power bank in hold
OL,4,Cluggage on a holiday flight?
OL,6,FHe added: "Whilst pilots and cabin
OL,7,Fcrew are trained to deal with any
OL,8,Fsituation, the best outcome is always
OL,9,Fprevention, which starts when
OL,10,Fpassengers pack their bags."
OL,12,FGiuseppe Capanna, product safety
OL,13,Fengineer at charity Electrical Safety
OL,14,FFirst, said power banks "can pose a
OL,15,Fserious fire risk if they become
OL,16,Fdamaged or are manufactured to a
OL,17,Fsubstandard level".
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@\O]vD@YOUyD@RO]
